{"tid":2094100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳弘毅：港區國安法可視為社會契約　不損港人尊嚴","createTime":"2020-07-04T10:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T16:21:09.000Z","uid":126889,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d30880ac48d8b6e37fb31ecfe5f51c669b2214fb","tid":2094100,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:36:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=396721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D396721&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=f5f117ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D396721&h=58677ce7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=396721</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】身兼基本法委員會委員的港大法律學院教授陳弘毅指，港區國安法條文可理解為中央為繼續實施一國兩制而提出社會契約，不會損害香港人的尊嚴。<br />\n<br />\n陳弘毅：「這契約要求香港市民履行一種最低的義務，就是不要逾越『一國』底線，這些要求並不太高，也並非過分，願意接受這些行為準則的香港市民，便能繼續在香港安居樂業。『一國兩制』中作為『兩制』的其中之一的香港的制度、價值和精神，只要不違反國安法定出的『一國』底線，便能夠繼續存在和發展。」<br />\n<br />\nHKU Law <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依D算係蛋頭學者定共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e481c6c392efa3ff697bccad21505a83f2105f","tid":2094100,"uid":126889,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:39:32.000Z","msg":"社會契約論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n防暴狗可以拋下書包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a806a29c22cb4620e12123d423e896aaf03386","tid":2094100,"uid":335434,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:42:41.000Z","msg":"Rousseau教識世人乜嘢叫「社會契約」<br />\n陳弘毅教授就身體力行教識世人乜嘢叫「社會契弟」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5edb9644bf85de2636cd58873e7dbdee6f35